Title: Establishes the managed long term care high acuity stabilization pool; appropriation
Summary: Establishes the managed long term care high acuity stabilization pool to support managed long term care plans that demonstrate high performance on quality measures established by the department and serve a disproportionately high share of members with complex long term care needs or high service utilization.
ActClause: AN ACT to establish the managed long term care high acuity stabilization pool; and making an appropriation therefor
